            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Limit Notifications</h4>
              <p class="description"> Disable unnecessary notifications to reduce the constant urge to check your phone. 
                Control when and how often you access social media to avoid feeling overwhelmed.</p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
