            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Curate Your Feed</h4>
              <p class="description">Follow accounts and communities that inspire, educate, and uplift you. 
                Unfollow or mute accounts that consistently make you feel negative emotions or impact your mental health negatively.</p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
            <div class="icon flex-shrink-0"><i class="bi bi-binoculars" style="color: #15bfbc;"></i></div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Limit Screen Time</h4>
              <p class="description">Set boundaries for yourself by allocating specific times for social media use. 
                Excessive screen time can lead to feelings of anxiety or stress. 
                Take breaks and disconnect regularly.</p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <div class="icon flex-shrink-0"><i class="bi bi-brightness-high" style="color: #f5cf13;"></i></div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="title">Turn on Grayscale</h4>
              <p class="description">You can reduce the visual cues on your phone that make you more prone to look at your screen by changing to grayscale. 
                There are some apps that use features on your devices to create an automation that switches grayscale on and off depending on when you need to focus more.</p>
            </div>
          </div><!-- End Service Item -->

          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
